Yobe State Governor, Mai Mala Buni, has congratulated Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu, for emerging as the presidential flag bearer of the All Progressives Congress. Governor Buni described Tinubu as a well-grounded politician who can lead the party to victory in the 2023 general election. He urged former aspirants to join hands with Tinubu to ensure the success of the party in the Presidential election. “The Primary is over, we should all rally around our Presidential candidate to ensure the party’s victory in the general election,” he said. Buni enjoined former aspirants to embrace the spirit of sportsmanship for the unity and success of the party.